DISCLAIMER FOR MENTAL HEALTH APPLICATION

This software is provided as a supportive tool and is NOT a substitute for
professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Users experiencing mental
health crises should immediately contact emergency services or crisis hotlines.

The authors and copyright holders assume no responsibility or liability for
any consequences resulting from use of this software. Always seek the guidance
of qualified health providers with any questions regarding mental health
conditions.

If you or someone you know is in crisis:
- Call 988 (Suicide & Crisis Lifeline) in the United States
- Text HOME to 741741 (Crisis Text Line)
- Call emergency services (911 in the US)
- Go to the nearest emergency room

This software collects no personal data and stores all information locally
on the user's device.
